% ================================================================
% SECTION B — "He is Alpha and Omega, He the source, the ending He"  (mm. 8-13)
% ================================================================
%
% mm. 8-9: "He is Alpha and Omega"
% Texture: antiphonal — SSAA leads alone, TTBB echoes
%
[V:1] D3/2 E/ F G | (F D3/2) E/ |
