% mm. 10-13: "He the source, the ending He"
% Texture: full 8 voices, sustained momentum
%
[V:1] F4 | F3/2 G/ A B A G | c2 d4 | (c A) B |
[V:2] A,4 | D3/2 E/ F G F E | A2 B4 | (A F) G |
[V:3] C4 | C3/2 C/ F F F E | F2 F4 | F2 D |
